d at your clinic depending on the service type."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What payment gateways are supported?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Virtual Practice supports leading payment gateways including Stripe, Plug'n Pay, Razor-pay and others, depending on your country and currency preferences."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I bill patients in different currencies?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, Multi-currency support lets you accept payments in your patient's local currency. You can define default and additional currencies under your Payment Settings."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I apply taxes to my services?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You can configure tax rates in the Payment Settings section. Taxes can be automatically applied to relevant services across locations."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients pay using credits or discounts?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, You can assign payment credits or service discounts to patients, which they can use fully or partially during checkout."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How are refunds handled in the Virtual Practice?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Refunds can be issued as patient credits instead of reversing online payments—helping you avoid payment gateway fees and maintain revenue flow."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Patients View Their Billing History?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, patients can view their billing history through the patient portal, promoting transparency and reducing support inquiries."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is it possible to track all payment statuses?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely, You can monitor every bill as paid, pending, or overdue in real time—across services, patients, and providers."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I export billing and revenue reports?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, Detailed billing reports can b